   Facility STEM-1 is a custom-built electron microscope optimized for
   imaging unstained biological molecules with minimal radiation damage.
   The STEM group at Brookhaven operates STEM-1 as a User Facility with
   NIH and DOE support. [DOE_NCRR_logos.jpg]

